```
from:
  type: Integer
  required: false

to:
  type: Integer
  required: false

limit:
  type: Integer
  required: false
  default: 100
```

Example:

```
lnm.futuresFixingHistory({
    limit: 20
  })
```

[`GET /futures/history/fixing`](https://docs.lnmarkets.com/api/v1/#futures-fixing-history) documentation for more details.

